'''Mark Coulier''' is a British make-up artist and special effects designer who worked on [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']] as an animatronic designer, and also acted in as the [[Malastare]] senator [[Aks Moe]], though professional voice actor [[Marc Silk]] was dubbed over him. He later worked as prosthetic make-up artist for [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']].

